Class Plant

java.lang.Object
Plant
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Plant
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
This is a plant. Its name corresponds with an image so we can make lots of happy little plants. Has the attributes needed for a good garden.
Author:
Raj Trivedi, Noah Hodgson, Luis Figueroa
